类 TdApi.EditMessageLiveLocation

  • 封闭类:
    TdApi

    public static class TdApi.EditMessageLiveLocation
extends TdApi.Function
    Edits the message content of a live location. Messages can be edited for a limited period of time specified in the live location. Returns the edited message after the edit is completed on the server side.

    Returns Message

        Creates a function, which edits the message content of a live location. Messages can be edited for a limited period of time specified in the live location. Returns the edited message after the edit is completed on the server side.

        Returns Message

        参数:
        chatId - The chat the message belongs to.
        messageId - Identifier of the message.
        replyMarkup - The new message reply markup; for bots only.
        location - New location content of the message; may be null. Pass null to stop sharing the live location.
        heading - The new direction in which the location moves, in degrees; 1-360. Pass 0 if unknown.
        proximityAlertRadius - The new maximum distance for proximity alerts, in meters (0-100000). Pass 0 if the notification is disabled.
